  "description": "<div class=\"g-container\">\n\t<h1 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px 40px; font-size: 1.571em; line-height: 1.4;\">\n\t\tQuiz</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"g-container story-body\">\n\t<div class=\"bodytext\" style=\"font-size: 1em;\">\n\t\t<div id=\"quiz-form\" style=\"font-size: 1em;\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0.86em 0px 0.43em; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.29;\">\n\t\t\t\tToday's Topic :&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Taking a course 大学课程相关表达</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<form action=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/apps/ifl/ukchina/quizengine\" method=\"post\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t\t\t\t<fieldset style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul id=\"quiz-questions\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 6px 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.71; display: inline-block; clear: both; color: rgb(13, 61, 99); width: 546px; background-color: rgb(255, 204, 102);\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 6px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t1. It was a very _________ course, but we managed to get through it.</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"radios\" style=\"font-size: 1em; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 6px; overflow: hidden; width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"1\" />&nbsp;strong</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"2\" />&nbsp;heavy</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"3\" />&nbsp;strict</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_1\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"4\" />&nbsp;demanding</label></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"question-image\"><img align=\"left\" alt=\"student and teacher\" border=\"0\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/learningenglish/quizzes/images/1340_courses/4141758_teach_150.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\" vspace=\"4\" width=\"150\" /></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 6px 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.71; display: inline-block; clear: both; color: rgb(13, 61, 99); width: 546px; background-color: rgb(255, 204, 102);\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 6px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t2. My boss has decided to send me to China to do a _________ course in Mandarin. It's very intensive - 8 hours every day for 10 days.</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"radios\" style=\"font-size: 1em; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 6px; overflow: hidden; width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_2\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"1\" />&nbsp;crash</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_2\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"2\" />&nbsp;fast</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_2\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"3\" />&nbsp;speed</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_2\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"4\" />&nbsp;high-speed</label></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"question-image\"><img align=\"left\" alt=\"China\" border=\"0\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/learningenglish/quizzes/images/1340_courses/4141958_china2_150.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\" vspace=\"4\" width=\"150\" /></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 6px 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.71; display: inline-block; clear: both; color: rgb(13, 61, 99); width: 546px; background-color: rgb(255, 204, 102);\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 6px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t3. I'm __________ a course in flower arranging next week; I thought it would be interesting and a good way to meet people.</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"radios\" style=\"font-size: 1em; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 6px; overflow: hidden; width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_3\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"1\" />&nbsp;doing</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_3\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"2\" />&nbsp;going on</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_3\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"3\" />&nbsp;taking</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_3\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"4\" />&nbsp;all of the above answers</label></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"question-image\"><img align=\"left\" alt=\"flowers\" border=\"0\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/learningenglish/quizzes/images/1340_courses/4142139_flowers_150x80.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\" vspace=\"4\" width=\"150\" /></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 6px 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.71; display: inline-block; clear: both; color: rgb(13, 61, 99); width: 546px; background-color: rgb(255, 204, 102);\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 6px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t4. If you apply to a university in the UK or Australia, you might get a ___________ offer of a place on the course; the university may require you to pass the IELTS exam or go on a short English language course.</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"radios\" style=\"font-size: 1em; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 6px; overflow: hidden; width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_4\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"1\" />&nbsp;condition</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_4\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"2\" />&nbsp;conditional</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_4\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"3\" />&nbsp;conditioned</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_4\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"4\" />&nbsp;conditioning</label></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"question-image\"><img align=\"left\" alt=\"taking an exam\" border=\"0\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/learningenglish/quizzes/images/1340_courses/4142532_exam_150.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\" vspace=\"4\" width=\"150\" /></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 6px 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.71; display: inline-block; clear: both; color: rgb(13, 61, 99); width: 546px; background-color: rgb(255, 204, 102);\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 6px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t5. Excuse me, I wonder if you could help me? Do you __________ Business English courses at your school?</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"radios\" style=\"font-size: 1em; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 6px; overflow: hidden; width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_5\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"1\" />&nbsp;run</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_5\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"2\" />&nbsp;give</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_5\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"3\" />&nbsp;study</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_5\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"4\" />&nbsp;all of the above answers</label></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"question-image\"><img align=\"left\" alt=\"business woman\" border=\"0\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/learningenglish/quizzes/images/1340_courses/4142841_business-woman_150x80.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\" vspace=\"4\" width=\"150\" /></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 6px 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.71; display: inline-block; clear: both; color: rgb(13, 61, 99); width: 546px; background-color: rgb(255, 204, 102);\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 6px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t6. Universities are now running more _________ courses than they did in the past; that is, courses that prepare you for a particular job or career path. I even saw a course for golf course management!</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"radios\" style=\"font-size: 1em; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 6px; overflow: hidden; width: 354px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_6\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"1\" />&nbsp;vocation</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_6\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"2\" />&nbsp;vocational</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_6\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"3\" />&nbsp;vacation</label><label style=\"float: left; width: 354px;\"><input name=\"answer_6\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\" type=\"radio\" value=\"4\" />&nbsp;vacational</label></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"question-image\"><img align=\"left\" alt=\"golf\" border=\"0\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/learningenglish/quizzes/images/1340_courses/414302_golf_150.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\" vspace=\"4\" width=\"150\" /></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</fieldset>\n\t\t\t</form>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<p>\n\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n\t<div id=\"checkanswer\">\n\t\t<input type=\"button\" value=\"核对答案\" /></div>\n\t<div id=\"tryagain\" style=\"display: none;\">\n\t\t<a href=\"#\"><b>Try Again</b></a></div>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<a href=\"#\"> </a></p>\n<!--\n\nfunction checkscore(myForm) {\n  var no_of_questions = '6',\n      i = 1,\n      score = 0;\n            \n        for (i = 1; i <= no_of_questions; i++) {\n            var myQuestion = document.quiz['q_' + i],\n                blank = true;\n    \n            for (var j = 0; j < myQuestion.length; j++) {\n            